trans-unit.source: Acts as the top of a two-level named hierarchy of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"></xref> collections.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som øverst i et navngitt hierarki for to nivåer med <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"> </xref> samlinger.

trans-unit.source: The RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection class is both a root-level <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collection and a container for a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Klassen RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection er både en primære <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>samlingen og en beholder for en <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection>samling.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>

trans-unit.source: These collections allow you to create named groups of more <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collections, each containing individual named <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objects.
trans-unit.target: Disse samlingene kan du opprette navngitt grupper med flere <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>samlinger, hver inneholdende person navnet <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings>objekter.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSection.PropertySettings%2A> property is a RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection object that contains all the properties defined within the `properties` subsection of the `profile` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSection.PropertySettings%2A>egenskapen er en RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection-objekt som inneholder alle egenskaper som er definert i den `properties` spørsmål for den `profile` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileSection.PropertySettings%2A>
